title: VIBRATE permission is not needed anymore.
message:
VIBRATE permission is not needed anymore.
The notification will vibrate the device without this permission.

title: Observer pattern replaced by events interfaces.
message: Observer pattern replaced by events interfaces.

title: In order to improve usability, when the fields get focus, the text is cleared.
message:
In order to improve usability, when the fields get focus, the text is cleared.
If the user left them empty, the initial value (00) is added.

title: A notification is displayed when the time is over.
message: A notification is displayed when the time is over.
